@DATABASE "Knight Lore"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - K - Knight Lore"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - K
                   ====================================

                                Knight Lore
                                ===========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(53567,0)"}          53567,0 
@{"Infinite Time " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(50205,0) ZXAMPoke(50206,0) ZXAMPoke(50207,0)"}          50205,0:50206,0:50207,0
@{"Stops Sundial " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(50084,201)"}          50084,201
@{"Objects = x   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49759,1)"}          49759,x (x= 1-255)


                         I don't know if the "Stop Sundial" POKE actually does
                         anything useful, but it was there, so I included it.

                         Nor did I know if the "Objects" POKE works. If it
                         does, then I would only put in a smaller amount of
                         objects to collect instead of a larger amount, as
                         the game only generates a set amount of objects at
                         set locations.. Don't take my word for it though..
                         I was always crap at this game....

                         Rastan.
@endnode
